Vhelenttain dde ho mogeancho dis (sentt vhelenttain dde). 14 februvari ho dis purai somvsarobhor vhelenttain dde mhunn monoitat. Hea disa mogi ekamekank 'bi mai velenttain' (mhojench mogi tum) oxem boroil'lem kardd dhaddttat.[1]
sentt vhelenttain

zanchea namvamn ho dis monoita to sentt vhelenttain kiristamv dhormacho romnacho raza klaiddiyon- 2 hannem vhelenttainachi kiristamv dhorma addchi xikounn polloun taka bondkhonnint ghalo. Ten'nachea kallant soinik bhorti khatir lognacher bondi ghal'li. Tori astana to aplea mogi cholyevangodda logn zalo. Tannem hem kloddiyrosachea hukmaadd kel'lean tannem taka 14 februvari disa mornnachi kheast formaili.[2]

vhelenttain zom-i kheast bhogtalo tachea zonela bhair vhailottachim khub zhaddam axil'lim. Tea zhaddanchem ek pan kaddun tacher tujea vhelenttainachi yad dour he xobd boroilem ani te pan bondkhonnichea efisorache kudd'dde cholyekodden dhaddlem. Hachem foll mhunn hachem foll mhunn mogachea xrodhdecher aesttoriache kudd'ddeponn drixttint bodlolem ani tika dispak laglem. Hi khobor soglleak patll'lli ani ten'nachean mogi tornatte chole- choleo ho dis 'lyuprkos' hea namvan monounk lagle. Fuddem 496t vorsa pop hannem somazache kudd'dde vicharosoronnek lagun tea utsovacher bondi haddli.[3]
protha

oxem mhonnttat, frebruvari mhoineant vosont ritunt tea kallant romi tornatte aplea mogi premikank magnni ghaltale oxi protha axil'li tamnni boroil'li mogachi chitt 14 februvarik dhaddttale. Hech prothek magir lhou lhou 'vhelenttain chitt' mhonnpak lagle. Fuddem hacho prochar vaddot gelo. Uprant vhelenttain karddom dhaddpachi protha soglleat poilim oxem torechem kardd jyuno februatt hannem boroilem oxem mhonnttat.

Kaim zannkaranchea motapromann he prothecho ani vhelemnottain hea namvan zaun gel'lea don sontancho toso kainch sombond na. Romon purann kothentoli mogeachi devi vhinos hicho cholo kyupiddochem chitr karddacher asta.Vhelenttainchea karddacher asta.

Sollavea xekddeant svitzhorolonddant sentt fransis ddi sels ef jineuha haka oxem dislem, kiristamv lok borech modeleat tanka xist laupa khatir tannem ten'na ostit'tvant axil'li lottri pod'dot bond keli. He lottri pod'dotin romon lok lAettri tiketticher sontanchi namvam ghaltale. Tornatte chole choleo chitteo kaddttali ani tea lAettrichea ddro promann vorsobhor tacheborobor somvsar korcho poddttalo.

Otthravea xenkddeant framsantleo tornatteo choleo aplea mogea choleachem namv kagdar boroun to kagod va chitt tachem fattir dosoitalim. Toxench modhy yugant choleo hollduvea rongache kopdde ghaltalim. Tachea motan hollduvo rong ho pun'nirmiticho, sukhi somvsaracho.

Vhelenttain dde hi protha londdon,inglondd, omerika,ittli hea dexant khub procharant asa. Bhartat hi protha brittix lokampasun aili. Aiz hi protha xarampasun gamvgireavatthara meren paulea. Poilichea kallant hea disa karddam dhaddttale. Sodeachea kallant kardda vangdda mogacho sondex axil'lim podam, sttof ttoiz va ugddasak urpasarkeo vosti ekamekank bhett dhaddttat.

